                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100606-101-victim804 t18100606-101-viclabel560"></join>, I live in Coventry court in the Haymarket. On the 4th upon between three and four in the afternoon, I was in <placeName id="t18100606-101-crimeloc561">St. James's-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18100606-101-crimeloc561" type="placeName" value="St. James's-street"></interp>
